instruction: Please provide a summary of the AI model's performance in agency prepayment modeling during the period of analysis.
output: During the period of analysis, the AI model successfully addressed the challenges of high dimensionality and high nonlinearity in agency prepayment modeling. By selecting appropriate modeling parameters, the length of the modeling process was reduced from months to hours. Overall, the AI model's performance was impressive and helped to improve the efficiency of the prepayment modeling process.
